Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,THE MARRIAGE OF TEACHER CURRY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the day of your wedding,\NI hope you don't get upset, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you a happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh...!\N- Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The blackboard is for study only!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't spoil it with anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the lesson immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you see the sun at\Nthe beginning of the summer,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the sky looks beautiful and very warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind comes in the fifth month,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and then the buds are fertilized{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and so it is every summer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie... Well, that 's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll gave her this bouqet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The bride will be very happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could see teacher Curry\Nwith a happy face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we'll celebrate it soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the teacher's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be bad that\Nteacher Curry suddenly smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be happy for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it delivered to Miss Mary directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want to congratulate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right now she went out with Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Went for a consultation about the new home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can give it to her myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We will take it to the residence\Nof the teacher Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll give it to Miss Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But we are going to Mr. Curry and Miss Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher will be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how his face looks when\Nhe talks to her on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go to the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten anything else important?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else important?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, something else is very important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The wedding settings are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Honeymoon equipment is arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the wedding ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I won't forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep it in my wedding\Ncoat pocket for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is complete now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh really? Oh really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something else you have forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't yet done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation seems strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What absurdity are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no wedding, be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be nervous\Njust before the wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home and sleep well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I will take you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go back alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well okay, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk about this thing\Nagain after the wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss Mary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Listen, Miss Mary...\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be a wedding tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you\Ndon't like Curry teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher Curry is already poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that he is shy and very nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's a nice person at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,John, don't say this to Miss Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,John, it is true that he is shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end he is a straight\Nperson and always smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He is also a very honest person with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After reading his favorite poem\NI can see his beautiful smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say this thing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Miss Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't abstain, you can talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am also good at listening to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father, listen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you suddenly ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I love your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you tell this to my mother directly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-why did you suddenly ask?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a secret!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, it's a beautiful morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the wedding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Curry's wedding today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best time for a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,John, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also Lassie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from you, you came early!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she in the waiting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you seen her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not good to see her before she dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't believe in superstitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it wasn't in the waiting room!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She may still be asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine, I'm sure she's still in her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See you later!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't come yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what should I write?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To Robert...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's 10 o'clock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}30 minutes left til the wedding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I feel that you helped me a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, teacher Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary? Hasn't she come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strange!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She should be wearing her dress now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, excuse me for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary has long gone before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't Mary come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to hear my answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't marry you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm serious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, I'm happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the father feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're John Carraclough's dog, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't enter the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment, give me this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To Robert Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a message from Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a message from Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the envelope quickly\Nand read the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally came!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The message is more important...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my child's wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the other side\Nof the earth you can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your nice fianc√©e?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she went to bring something\Nshe had just forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a wedding dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So it should take longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a calamity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Read it quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the late submission of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mary's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... she went to bring something\Nshe has forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Read the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The priest will come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your father yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck, if I knew that, I wouldn't have\Nthought of being a husband to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This... I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mr Rice! Teacher Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to have completely\Nforgotten the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The guests must've arrived by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I''m sure that teacher Curry\Nwill come, and he is scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you do this good work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Never doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will marriage be so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't she come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday we had no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done! Read it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will wait for you in the place\Nof our first memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We go also!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary! Mary! Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To the memory of xxx to your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,School is not on this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher Curry went on the wrong path!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mary wrote the place\Nwhere their memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he would know\Nthat right away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He never knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Curly teacher is running fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, I have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to play with you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is a precious marriage ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she come to such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something else I forgot to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's about wallpaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, I also like the green color!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallpaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always make sure not to bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to bother me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fix the flaws all my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sort my clothes well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be sure to brush\Nmy teeth after eating meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be very careful not to eat messy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also clean the place after cutting my nails...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He act like children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be angry with me and marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not angry on these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In this place we had the first\Nconversation between us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to deliver the school trip bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you said this is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you remembered the memories\Nthat we have come to here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, actually I went to Berry Forest near by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Lassie took my box...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, give me the box, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten the most important\Nthing you should say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that you would talk about the same\Nsubject that took place yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many times have\NI tried to ask you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing I forgot, that I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are nice and good at cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are also interested in books
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and also the wallpaper's color...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to say this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage between men and women means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the beginning\Nof the establishment of the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Other than that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because you are a professional player!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your white fingers are clicking on the piano,\Nand then the melody comes out beautifully!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sign of the size of our relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a word I wanted to hear from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is what I want of your heart\Nbefore it comes out of your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me with all your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hear you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally you managed to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You never told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept your marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, I wish you a happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, don't neglect your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you brush your teeth well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't notice these things to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
